{
  "id": "prophecy-scroll",
  "name": "预言卷轴",
  "category": "prophecy",
  "description": "一张神秘的预言卷轴，带有占卜和命运元素",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "random",
    "probability": 0.015,
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "setting",
        "operator": "contains",
        "value": "预言|命运|占卜|神秘|未来|宿命",
        "description": "预言或神秘场景可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "prophecyId": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "预言编号"
    },
    "title": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "预言标题"
    },
    "prophet": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "预言者"
    },
    "date": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "预言日期"
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 400,
      "description": "预言内容"
    },
    "interpretation": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "解读提示"
    },
    "prophecyType": {
      "type": "string",
      "default": "命运",
      "options": ["命运", "警示", "启示", "预言"],
      "description": "预言类型"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一张预言卷轴的内容。\n\n背景信息：\n- 预言者：{{prophet}}\n- 预言类型：{{prophecyType}}\n- 场景：{{scene}}\n\n要求：\n1. 使用神秘预言风格的语言\n2. 内容要带有隐喻和象征\n3. 可以包含模糊但意味深长的预言\n4. 字数控制在150-300字之间\n\n请直接输出预言内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "prophecy",
    "colors": ["#1a1a2e", "#e94560", "#ffd700"],
    "mood": "神秘预言"
  },
  "rarity": "epic",
  "collectible": true
}